<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.7">
<l>tarukki ṉālcamaṇ ceytu cōṟutaṇ tayiri ṉāltira ḷaimi ṭaṟṟiṭai</l>
<l>nerukku vāralak kaṇa tukaṇṭeṉ neñcamaṉpāy</l>
<l>maruṭkaḷ vaṇṭukaḷ pāṭum vēṅkaṭam kōyil koṇṭata ṉōṭum vāṉiṭai</l>
<l>yarukkaṉ mēviniṟ pāṟka ṭimaittoḻil pūṇṭāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My companion heart, seeing the quarreling of those Jains</l>
<l rend="indent">who mash into their throats</l>
<l>Lumps of rice with cool curds, acting with arrogance,</l>
<l rend="indent">today you assumed the duty of service</l>
<l>To the one who, having a temple at Vēṅkaṭam where bees sing</l>
<l rend="indent">songs of wonderment,</l>
<l>Also endures dwelling there [like] the sun in the heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
